# Big Countries

Return the name, population, and area of countries that are considered "big", defined as:
- Area ≥ 3,000,000 km², or
- Population ≥ 25,000,000


Table: World

| Column      | Type    |
|-------------|---------|
| name        | varchar |
| continent   | varchar |
| area        | int     |
| population  | int     |
| gdp         | bigint  |


